Package: issuetriager
Type: Package
Title: Automated Triage of Support Issues
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Elliot", "Murphy", , "elliot@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7473-8081")),
    person(, "RStudio, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: This R package contains functions to analyze text of GitHub issues
    in order to do some automatic issue triage. This library is packaged inside
    a GitHub action and can be combined with other actions to do things like label
    issues, close issues, and notify slack channels.
